{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<progress>：进度指示元素","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML</strong>中的<strong><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></strong>元素用来显示一项任务的完成进度。虽然规范中没有规定该元素具体如何显示，浏览器开发商可以自己决定，但通常情况下，该元素都显示为一个进度条形式。</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/progress.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用上下文","title":"使用上下文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><strong>使用策略                </strong>流文本 (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>),&nbsp;短文本 (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a>)\n<strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Content categories (en-US)</a>     </strong>可标记内容，可触摸内容\n\n<strong>有效内容                </strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Phrasing content (en-US)</a>, 其中在它的后代中不能包含\n<strong>Permitted content</strong>      <code>&lt;progress&gt;</code>元素。\n\n<strong>标签省略                </strong>不可以，不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。\n<strong>Tag omission</strong>\n\n<strong>有效的父元素</strong>             任何可以包裹短文本 (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a>) 的元素。\n\n<strong>隐式元素                </strong><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#progressbar\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">progressbar</a></code>\n<strong>ARIA role</strong>\n\n<strong>有效的辅助元素            </strong>无\n<strong>ARIA roles</strong>\n\n<strong>DOM 接口</strong>                <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code></a>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>和其他的 HTML 元素一样，该元素具有<a href=\"/zh-cn/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" rel=\"internal\">全局属性</a>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"max\"><a id=\"attr-max\" href=\"#attr-max\"><b><code>max</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>该属性描述了这个<code>progress</code>元素所表示的任务一共需要完成多少工作。</dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><a id=\"attr-value\" href=\"#attr-value\"><b><code>value</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>该属性用来指定该进度条已完成的工作量。如果没有<code>value 属性</code>,则该进度条的进度为\"不确定\",也就是说，进度条不会显示任何进度，你无法估计当前的工作会在何时完成 (比如在下载一个未知大小的文件时，下载对话框中的进度条就是这样的).</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>你可以使用<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/-moz-orient\"><code>orient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>属性来指定该进度条的显示方向是横向 (默认) 还是纵向.CSS 伪类<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:indeterminate\"><code>:indeterminate</code></a>可以用来匹配那些不确定的进度条。</p>\n</div>\n\n<dl>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_接口","title":"DOM 接口","isH3":false,"content":"<p>该元素实现了<code><a href=\"/zh-cn/docs/DOM/HTMLProgressElement\" title=\"zh-cn/DOM/HTMLProgressElement\">HTMLProgressElement</a></code>接口。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>progress</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>70<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">max</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>70 %<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>progress</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例子\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"200\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>在 Mac OS X 上，显示的进度条如下：</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"progress-1.png\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/4946/=progress-1.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>在 Windows 上，显示的进度条如下：</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"progress-firefox.JPG\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/6031/=progress-firefox.JPG\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#the-progress-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;progress&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sec-forms.html#the-progress-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;progress&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>起始定义</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.progress","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:indeterminate\"><code>:indeterminate</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/-moz-orient\"><code>-moz-orient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/::-moz-progress-bar\"><code>::-moz-progress-bar</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>::-ms-fill</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/::-webkit-progress-bar\"><code>::-webkit-progress-bar</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/::-webkit-progress-value\"><code>::-webkit-progress-value</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/::-webkit-progress-inner-element\"><code>::-webkit-progress-inner-element</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"概述"},{"text":"使用上下文","id":"使用上下文"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"DOM 接口","id":"dom_接口"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"HTML中的<progress>元素用来显示一项任务的完成进度。虽然规范中没有规定该元素具体如何显示，浏览器开发商可以自己决定，但通常情况下，该元素都显示为一个进度条形式。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<progress>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<progress>: The Progress Indicator element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<progress>: Elemento indicador de progreso","locale":"es","nativ